## ğŸš€ Installation

### 1. Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/ai-sales-agent.git
cd ai-sales-agent
```

### 2. Install dependencies

```bash
npm install
```

### 3. Setup environment variables

Create a `.env` file:

```env
OPENAI_API_KEY=your-openai-key
WHATSAPP_API_URL=https://your-whatsapp-api/send
DEFAULT_COUNTRY=US
```

> ğŸ’¡ `WHATSAPP_API_URL` must point to a working API that can send WhatsApp messages (e.g., [Chat-API](https://chat-api.com/) or [WATI](https://www.wati.io/))

